{"tid":1728743,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"數百中大生寫信向受阻市民道歉","createTime":"2019-11-17T04:01:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-17T05:58:29.000Z","uid":25558,"like":31,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"66c0f675b42a752e9badcce1ada533e16ede0efb","tid":1728743,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T04:01:33.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20191117/KPVH6YHM6Y52UJPOF6DQS22EUE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20191117%2FKPVH6YHM6Y52UJPOF6DQS22EUE%2F&d=PiwLpsDni%2BEQUOLZDbBUz85Q2JFdPMmcxM5Tq6mQO7A%3D&h=bdc143e3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20191117%2FKPVH6YHM6Y52UJPOF6DQS22EUE%2F&h=7c15b91e\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20191117/KPVH6YHM6Y52UJPOF6DQS22EUE/</a><br />\n<br />\n數百中大生寫信向受阻市民道歉<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】中大保衞戰導致貫通新界南北的吐露港公路癱瘓，對公眾造成不便。數百名中大學生寫親筆信（圖），向公眾解釋行動，並向受影響人士致歉。他們表示，中大生的行動源於漠視民意的政府，阻礙道路乃無可奈何之計，「不求支持，但求理解」。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：稱行動毋須上報 官媒速刪報道<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20191117/large/1573922189_65aa.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20191117%2Flarge%2F1573922189_65aa.gif&h=6620749e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n中大生以「一隻高牆前的雞蛋」署名撰寫道歉信，盼市民體諒抗爭行動。<br />\nAppleDaily<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n網民支持：永不割席<br />\n<br />\n「對不起，令您的交通受影響。在此向您致以最誠摯的歉意。」中大生的道歉信解釋，他們11.11起發動的抗爭行動，一切都歸咎於漠視民意的政府。信中列舉了多宗事故，包括6.12政府把和平集會定性為暴動；6.16二百萬人和平遊行，政府視而不見；7.21警黑合作無差別攻擊市民；8.31血染太子站；10.1實彈射向學生；11.8警方阻礙消防向墮樓科大學生救援。這群署名「一隻高牆前的雞蛋」的中大生指出，每個周末，警方都向長者、小孩、孕婦、毛孩發射無數催淚彈、橡膠子彈、布袋彈及實彈。他們解釋，阻礙通路乃無可奈何之計，目的只是要高官立即回應訴求，「造成不便，不好意思，懇求您們能體諒」。<br />\n<br />\n中大生的誠意獲網民支持，有人留言說：「做錯嘢嘅，係政權、係一眾建制派，真香港人係不會對前線有怨言嘅。前線嘅無私付出、多謝都來不及！永不割席。」有網民回應：「不要對唔住，你哋付出生命前途，根本不是你們錯。你哋好好，感謝你們年輕人。我哋廢老幫唔到你哋年輕人。本人好希望你哋小心保護自己，互相保護，團結一致。香港人係好高質素，加油！」<br />\n<br />\n■記者蔡元貴<br />\n==============<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n仆街政府<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa5c47556f07b63b472f6d32d13087bc564c2640","tid":1728743,"uid":294173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T04:03:07.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cf90d8581fedd9535251f743d5a8a69e30564c1e","tid":1728743,"uid":297230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T04:03:45.000Z","msg":"<strong>他們在打的是「中共政權保衛戰」，而你們僅僅是在打「香港生活方式保衛戰」</strong><a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1728140/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1728140/page/1</a><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;-</span><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">（一） Be Water(水聚散) 不能變為Be Castle（碉堡戰、陣地戰）</span></strong><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">對付Be Water，<strong>第一就是分化</strong>，<strong>把勇武派、和理非派拆分</strong>，<strong>第二步是下餌，引誘勇武派進入「必守的陣地」</strong>，刺激他們建立碉堡，最好所有的勇武派都集中進入少數陣地（例如四所大學），然後<strong>隔絕、撒網、一舉成擒</strong>。</span><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">（二） 從「誰才是暴徒」辯論陷阱脫身</span></strong><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">港人對抗港府還算旗鼓相當，畢竟兩邊都是被法治洗禮過的香港人，<strong>但是港人對付中共的無底綫宣傳統戰技能</strong>，坦白說，<strong>還是太嫩</strong>。世人關心香港事態的焦點從「港人要自由、要自治」，變成「人民和政府誰才是暴力方」的辯論，這正是<strong>北京</strong>要製造的<strong>焦點轉移</strong>。</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>（三） 一切回歸三個字 &ndash; 真普選</strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">核心訴求只有一個：真普選，一切口號、行動、宣傳，都環繞真普選這單一訴求展開，<strong>這樣，世界聽得懂，連中國內地人民都聽得懂</strong>。<br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"be976872cafc8c9b8a6dd00acc94556f456faa0e","tid":1728743,"uid":308440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T04:04:43.000Z","msg":"邏去連儂牆做文宣, 呢part 各區少都可憐."},{"pid":"28031abbbc83c30afece293296b212b1a5b94cfd","tid":1728743,"uid":175159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T04:05:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mxt1cwB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fmxt1cwB.jpg&h=856c1eeb&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pYTgLRB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpYTgLRB.jpg&h=c4c69382&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"004ee496d6859653a0e641fa3bcc45a73d428c90","tid":1728743,"uid":68430,"like":3,"dislike":9,"score":-6,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T04:06:53.000Z","msg":"失左民心 冇咁意得番"},{"pid":"9bfa0848a92bcb3eb3f3121048475e53c54235e4","tid":1728743,"uid":168097,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"004ee496d6859653a0e641fa3bcc45a73d428c90","tid":1728743,"uid":68430,"like":3,"dislike":9,"score":-6,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T04:06:53.000Z","msg":"失左民心 冇咁意得番"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T04:08:04.000Z","msg":"你老母就失人心"},{"pid":"cb69c4366b96008591f2e5be945b7a84d95e0472","tid":1728743,"uid":168097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9bfa0848a92bcb3eb3f3121048475e53c54235e4","tid":1728743,"uid":168097,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"004ee496d6859653a0e641fa3bcc45a73d428c90","tid":1728743,"uid":68430,"like":3,"dislike":9,"score":-6,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T04:06:53.000Z","msg":"失左民心 冇咁意得番"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T04:08:04.000Z","msg":"你老母就失人心"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T04:08:21.000Z","msg":"民"},{"pid":"e4e1e08ec445473f098e80fe36c4a9637f422e1a","tid":1728743,"uid":19126,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T04:14:34.000Z","msg":"要體諒既一直體